<CENTER><P><FONT SIZE=+1>Willis Corroon is a world-wide knowledge-based
company providing risk management solutions, risk transfer expertise and
specialised consultancy services. Our primary purpose is to help organisations
to survive and succeed through the effective management of their risk exposures.
We seek leadership positions in the market sectors we choose to serve and
to become the long term partner of choice, delivering outstanding value
to both clients and risk carriers. </FONT></P></CENTER>

<CENTER><TABLE CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=0 >
<TR>
<TD align=left>Willis Corroon Group is one of the world's largest insurance
and reinsurance brokers and risk management consultants.<BR>
<BR>
Our goal is to meet clients' needs in managing and reducing the cost of
risk to the highest attainable standard. <BR>
</TD>

<TD align=center>
<CENTER><P><A HREF="logomap.map"><IMG ISMAP SRC="logomap.gif" LOWSRC="logomapbw.gif" BORDER=0 HEIGHT=295 WIDTH=344></A>
</P></CENTER>
</TD>

<TD align=right>The Group's head office is in London. In the USA its principal
office is in Nashville. The Group has offices in major cities all over
the world, being represented by more than 9,000 staff in over 261 offices
in some 74 countries. <BR>
<BR>
Each year the Group handles insurance premiums on behalf of its clients
of over &pound;7 billion, or $11 billion.<BR>
</TD>
</TR>
</TABLE></CENTER>

